Defence completes preliminary investigation into Waterkloof Air Force Base fire incident 26 January 2022 The South African National Defence Force completes preliminary investigation into the fire incident that broke out at Air Force Base Waterkloof on Sunday, 23 January 2022 The South African National Defence Force (SANDF) can confirm that the preliminary investigation into the fire that broke out at Air Force Base Waterkloof on Sunday, 23 January 2022 has been completed. And, the report will be compiled and given to the Chief of the SANDF to apply his mind on it. When the Chief of the SANDF has fully studied the report, and gave his guidelines, it will then be communicated to all members of the media as earlier promised. To this effect, a Board of Inquiry has been convened. Issued by Brigadier General Andries Mokoena Mahapa, Director Defence Corporate Communication, Department of Defence, 26 January 2022   